
http request response animation is possible only with custom show
Whole page run simultaneously in custom page. You cant run a portion with one button click, 
and another portion with another button click.
To do so you have to mak to separate custom page.
custom slide cant be linked with any shape. It can be linked with action button only.

To run a custom page in loop, do following in powerpoint 2016
a> Slide show tab->setup slide show-> Loop continiously until escape
b>Click on the custom show page-> go to transition tab->under advanced slide portion, check after 00:00:00
c>Do not set until end of the slide in timing window of any animation
d>Hide de the custom slide
e> TAke an actin button on any other page, and link the custom show with that button (check return)

